Build instructions for openSUSE Factory
---------------------------------------

# Download installer (required for building packages)
osc service dr

# Build kernel module RPM
# 64bit
osc build openSUSE_Factory x86_64 nvidia-gfxG04.spec
osc build openSUSE_Factory x86_64 nvidia-uvm-gfxG04.spec
# 32bit
osc build openSUSE_Factory i586 nvidia-gfxG04.spec

# Build Driver RPM
# 64bit
osc build openSUSE_Factory x86_64 x11-video-nvidiaG04.spec
# 32bit
osc build openSUSE_Factory i586 x11-video-nvidiaG04.spec
